# Dashboard JSON files go here.
# scripts/provision-grafana.sh will load every *.json file in this directory
# into Grafana via the /api/dashboards/import endpoint.
#
# To add a dashboard:
#   1. Build/export it in the Grafana UI (Dashboard → Share → Export → Save to file)
#   2. Drop the JSON file here
#   3. Run: scripts/provision-grafana.sh
